<section id="selecting-and-changing-the-database-connection" version="5.0" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
                                                                           xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
                                                                           xmlns:xl="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" >
  <title>Selecting and changing the database connection</title>
  <orderedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        You can change the database you are connected to by selecting:
        
        <para>
          <emphasis role="menuPath">Test</emphasis>--&gt;<emphasis role="menuPath">Select database</emphasis>.
        </para>
      </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        In the dialog that appears, select the database you want to
        use and enter your username and password.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </orderedlist>
</section>